data.title: OASIS IN CARACAS CONFIRMED!!!
data.meta_description: The L4e forum is the web's most popular forum discussing English rock band Oasis and its members, Liam and Noel Gallagher as well as music, sports and pop culture
data.text:

Post by Rainmaker on

Oasis are returning for the 2 time ( they came in 2001) to Venezuela, with a concert at the UCV soccer stadium with a capacity of 30000 persons. The concert is the 28th of april and the tickets go on sale tomorrow
